    excerpt: "\ud83d\udc69\u200d\ud83d\udcbc Women-Owned Business Grants 2025: $2.1B Female Entrepreneur Revolution\n    \n      \n        \ud83c\udfc6 Top Women Business Programs\n        \n          \u2022 SBA ...",
    category: "Demographic-Specific",
